September 2009 collapse ==
On 8 September 2009, McErlaine was admitted to hospital after he collapsed with a massive brain aneurysm at the age of 41.
McErlaine was in a coma for nine weeks, and spent six and a half months in hospital, before being discharged to continue to recover at home.
